rows.NAME: Type
rows.DATA_ADDRESS:
(CASE 
	WHEN [#~alias#].`transfer_transaction_id` IS NOT NULL AND [#~alias#].`amount_booked` > 0 THEN "TRANSFER_IN"
	WHEN [#~alias#].`transfer_transaction_id` IS NOT NULL AND [#~alias#].`amount_booked` <= 0 THEN "TRANSFER_OUT"
	WHEN [#~alias#].`amount_booked` > 0 THEN "DEPOSIT" 
	WHEN [#~alias#].`amount_booked` <= 0 THEN "WITHDRAWAL"
END)
